QuestData.Title: WANTED: Lady Naz'jess
QuestData.Description:
Wanted for attacks against the Alliance!
Lady Naz'jess is responsible for leading several raids and ambushes against our soldiers. Extreme caution advised!
Upon completion of the mission, report to Lieutenant Hawkins for commendation.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve the head of Lady Naz'jess.
